    "name": "Paper Battlefield",
    "steam_appid": 3150030,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to <i>Paper Battlefield</i>, a strategy game where warfare takes place in a drawn world bound by the limits of a notebook! Experience a unique real-time strategy experience where every battle unfolds on the pages of a sketchbook, and all your units and structures are drawn with ink! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Battle on the Page:</strong> Engage in dynamic real-time strategy battles on a whimsical notebook battlefield. Watch as your tactical decisions come to life amidst doodles and sketches.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Resource Management:</strong> Gather ink to fuel your military might. Manage resources efficiently to build a formidable base, craft powerful units, and improve their effectiveness.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Base Building:</strong> Construct and upgrade your base with a variety of structures. Design your base layout strategically to fend off enemy attacks and ensure a steady supply of resources.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hire and Command Units:</strong> Recruit a diverse array of drawn combat units, each with unique characteristics. Command your units with precision, utilizing their strengths to dominate the battlefield.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Develop Strategies:</strong> Adapt your strategies as the battle unfolds. Each game is a new challenge, with unpredictable scenarios.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the battle in <i>Paper Battlefield</i> and draw your path to victory!</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 俄语, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
